text: Most shops are closed on Sunday. Good thing that the shop I wanted to visit still open on Sunday and parking was available at my visit. Per entry is $2.8 on Sunday. It seems only small parking lots here. Only B1, B2, and B3. I wonder how would it fits on weekday for parking here since it has 32 levels up.
Suprisingly found this massage offer very good massage. Price affordable and the new girl Cindy massage was good if you like hard massage.
Checked out a new dance club called Alpha. One of the best clubs with exhilarating ambience and awesome music.

There are eateries and 711 convenient store. This is an office tower.
It has an overhead pedestrian crossing linked with the opposite building.
During weekend and public holiday the city area is very quiet.

Easy access. Fuss Free Quiet Lift. Oxley Tower is at the traffic cross junction, exit F from Tanjung Pagar MRT. It is a prominent place so easy to ask for any security guard at any building to direct you to Oxley. V good experience coming here.
